message: Corrected controversy section. Paster Johns was found not guilty.
Principle section vandalism corrected. No Ms Donald even at school.
I actually go to the school. There is no Mrs Mcdonald even at the school.
/* Notable Residents */  Nathan Beaves is certainly not a notable resident.
More information on school rowing program
Icy pole only refers to a particular  ice block (oddly enough called "Icy pole". Also, having lived in Australia my whole life, I can say that "Granny trolley" and "Shopping jeep" are never used.
Added a reference where required. Also corrected vandalism.
Alan Sampson as principal? Nice try vandal.
